    "updated_at": "2015-08-26T01:07:58Z",
    "body": "When you run `electron .` you're running your app with electron's default menu items and accelerators built in. When you run it as a package, you'll need to add them yourself into your main process. \n\nSee https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/atom/browser/default_app/main.js as an example. \n"
